jmath.types

Class Complex

  • java.lang.Object
    • jmath.types.MObject
      • jmath.types.Complex

  • public class Complex
extends MObject
    Class for performing mathematics with complex values. A single object of this class represents a single number which is the sum of a real number, and an imaginary number
